{"tid":325203,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"走音版 你,好不好 唱歌撚","createTime":"2017-07-17T05:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T18:49:23.000Z","uid":51261,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0db483fd415e7e0285b01d8e4a01266d5ba019","tid":325203,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kg2.qq.com/node/play?s=bP9WcIbCasCEYbPq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkg2.qq.com%2Fnode%2Fplay%3Fs%3DbP9WcIbCasCEYbPq&d=lPKRRz6ssMTRD7aqGbf%2B%2FTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a6308f4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kg2.qq.com/node/play?s=bP9WcIbCasCEYbPq</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從小到中學 我一直無係人面前唱個歌 因為一直覺得自已唱得好難聽 但grad 左後 發覺自已真係好鐘意，而家暑假 我從上個月係屋企到而家不斷唱 日日自已一個係屋企唱幾粒鐘。。。毒<br />\n<br />\n最近開始一直唸，想話試下一次參加一次歌唱比賽 拎下經驗 練緊<br />\n<br />\n利申 努力學緊唱歌 <br />\n努力上緊高音"},{"pid":"62cfa0e6fc3d87609d09a3331a4a11658c9ba7b2","tid":325203,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"5661ba20c446fa1ceed99a456e54ab3afbc2baae","tid":325203,"uid":106967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打加油"},{"pid":"658ab527799050d005d6b7579b2ea154c4216fb1","tid":325203,"uid":1227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"玩下拍子機，我聽落好似句句都未準備好就唱"},{"pid":"53556c7a2794dc964a261a6679e419821630921b","tid":325203,"uid":43834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96758b6a701fe8eda8ebb2aeb0ffc2460b79d50","tid":325203,"uid":43834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:23:03.000Z","msg":"哪來的勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f75341deb378724fd1837d3c996135b9898ad8","tid":325203,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ae650b9a29707c0494e7da1fff273a6bc25a6c","tid":325203,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:24:26.000Z","msg":"好撚好聽‼️"},{"pid":"1de1cc1afda1d4929fb972a15b328eb89e7d6b23","tid":325203,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油"},{"pid":"edb4e9fd2965b13bd594aa06423c6582208b78ff","tid":325203,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3caeb2e70b51b4956648c314bcd04f98e3261736","tid":325203,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"我練好d拍子 再黎過 thanks 巴打"},{"pid":"88e648e33af8e69fd5a943b8f351ddc86c98af28","tid":325203,"uid":175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"個人意見<br />\n睇多幾次首歌<br />\n認住個音先<br />\n高音上唔到唔好格硬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247be5ff76d43f31e31433f9da6b7953d9f4204b","tid":325203,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:42:37.000Z","msg":"聽到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3742be7d5265939b32e47b39b6ebcf88d5e399a5","tid":325203,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kg2.qq.com/node/play?s=r9PvUQrlwXmarreC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkg2.qq.com%2Fnode%2Fplay%3Fs%3Dr9PvUQrlwXmarreC&d=lPKRRz6ssMTRD7aqGbf%2B%2FTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a963d7a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kg2.qq.com/node/play?s=r9PvUQrlwXmarreC</a><br />\n呢首我練左好多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你還要我怎樣 薛之x"},{"pid":"4a542f9c7b319c92fb4c7f6f47fe7f2517216054","tid":325203,"uid":28028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://kg2.qq.com/node/play?s=r9PvUQrlwXmarreC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkg2.qq.com%2Fnode%2Fplay%3Fs%3Dr9PvUQrlwXmarreC&d=lPKRRz6ssMTRD7aqGbf%2B%2FTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a963d7a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kg2.qq.com/node/play?s=r9PvUQrlwXmarreC</a><br />\n呢首我練左好多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你還要我怎樣 薛之x</blockquote><br />\n不如唱返廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a5141a65fe2a99ccbd75000e51ef2025c07bb0","tid":325203,"uid":123301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:35:40.000Z","msg":"開頭都勉強覺得正常唱k質素<br />\n去到高潮位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f18e52c7b77dbf2c5623feb1238318ab10901ca","tid":325203,"uid":84059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:55:59.000Z","msg":"持之以恆係好<br />\n但如果方法錯 練一萬個鐘都係錯<br />\n<br />\n就咁聽應該要由大舊野執起<br />\n拍子係一大問題<br />\n我唔知係你錄音搞到delay定係你慣左聽到要唱喇你先開始ready你既肌肉去唱<br />\n每一句你都好固定咁慢左開始<br />\n<br />\n同埋高音只係形容緊個pitch<br />\n你要唱唔同歌既高音都要學識唱到唔同既sound quality<br />\n呢樣好難好概括咁教你<br />\n但絕對唔係眯埋眼肉緊就上到高音<br />\n咁樣練唔會有成果 如果傷聲就仲衰<br />\n你話學緊唱歌 係自學定有跟老師？<br />\n有老師教會安全啲既<br />\n但係坊間呃飯食既都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你有specific某首歌某個位想唱得好啲可以係度問<br />\n逐個位執一步一步黎應該會慢慢有進步"},{"pid":"d768a517927499e50bad134b8e6e35f59e677358","tid":325203,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>持之以恆係好<br />\n但如果方法錯 練一萬個鐘都係錯<br />\n<br />\n就咁聽應該要由大舊野執起<br />\n拍子係一大問題<br />\n我唔知係你錄音搞到delay定係你慣左聽到要唱喇你先開始ready你既肌肉去唱<br />\n每一句你都好固定咁慢左開始<br />\n<br />\n同埋高音只係形容緊個pitch<br />\n你要唱唔同歌既高音都要學識唱到唔同既sound quality<br />\n呢樣好難好概括咁教你<br />\n但絕對唔係眯埋眼肉緊就上到高音<br />\n咁樣練唔會有成果 如果傷聲就仲衰<br />\n你話學緊唱歌 係自學定有跟老師？<br />\n有老師教會安全啲既<br />\n但係坊間呃飯食既都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你有specific某首歌某個位想唱得好啲可以係度問<br />\n逐個位執一步一步黎應該會慢慢有進步</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打提醒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自學啊 出面學唱歌好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0226dd493fb424fde0f198183a303f6d165e0a00","tid":325203,"uid":1638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:08:04.000Z","msg":"聽到都覺得失戀"},{"pid":"7f3d72a4c8bc03a1e931f5b79489acf85dc51766","tid":325203,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8110db4ab6b4c930e1eaf59ff1a70a44467bc636","tid":325203,"uid":672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:13:00.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪喊住唱,好有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2999015a1f93c23a6a4405c32a6ae9cb0ae2f3","tid":325203,"uid":51261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打係咪喊住唱,好有感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係就咁唱 起身 有d唔夠氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b7ce276b65fa25303c285c6e16b5709e086351","tid":325203,"uid":16777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"把聲好有感情 係技巧差啲<br />\n唱得出個種失戀人既感覺 聽者傷心<br />\n巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebbdc1c714034cdceb0e4e0e9288b98fe71ad7e","tid":325203,"uid":84059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>持之以恆係好<br />\n但如果方法錯 練一萬個鐘都係錯<br />\n<br />\n就咁聽應該要由大舊野執起<br />\n拍子係一大問題<br />\n我唔知係你錄音搞到delay定係你慣左聽到要唱喇你先開始ready你既肌肉去唱<br />\n每一句你都好固定咁慢左開始<br />\n<br />\n同埋高音只係形容緊個pitch<br />\n你要唱唔同歌既高音都要學識唱到唔同既sound quality<br />\n呢樣好難好概括咁教你<br />\n但絕對唔係眯埋眼肉緊就上到高音<br />\n咁樣練唔會有成果 如果傷聲就仲衰<br />\n你話學緊唱歌 係自學定有跟老師？<br />\n有老師教會安全啲既<br />\n但係坊間呃飯食既都唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你有specific某首歌某個位想唱得好啲可以係度問<br />\n逐個位執一步一步黎應該會慢慢有進步</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打提醒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自學啊 出面學唱歌好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋試下揀啲難度冇咁高既練習先<br />\n你一首歌有七八成都唱唔到/唱唔好係好難去進步<br />\n可能有首歌你大部分時間都唱得舒服既<br />\n係最尾有粒高音上極都上唔到<br />\n就可以重點拎出黎練習<br />\n以後其他歌遇到呢類型問題都會易啲解決"},{"pid":"513b954c934a4adb1e9d0d0e57a1451e9b781b3d","tid":325203,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T08:28:45.000Z","msg":"巴打你係咪喉嚨卡痰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}